snippet.title: Space Pioneer | Official Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Play NOW! 
iOS: http://bit.ly/SpacePioneerAppStore
ANDROID: http://bit.ly/SpacePioneerGooglePlay

Explore the galaxy as an intergalactic bounty hunter. Discover new planets, chart incredible worlds and exterminate any aliens that stand in your way in this hostile top-down free to play shooter.
